Description:
BRAND NEW IN OFFICER
"Buy in the 3809 postcode with a fresh build that's ready to move in today."
(Directions located at the bottom of the write-up)
Located opposite the pristine lake in Arcadia and right next to parkland the property at Zara Court is perfect for those that wish to be close to amenities. Walking distance to schools, shops and train station this property is earmarked as a wonderful investment or first home. And given that it's brand new, this property will save you $$$. As a first home buyer you can expect the full saving on stamp duty and the $10,000 rebate for a new build. As an investor you can expect the full seven year schedule for depreciation. There are countless other benefits as well including the house itself that features:
- Three bedrooms, master with en-suite and walk-in robe;
- Open plan living/dining room;
- Modern kitchen with stone benchtops;
- Heating and cooling;
- Double car remote garage with internal access;
- Wrap-around balcony with views overlooking the parkland and lake;
- Premier location among the complex.
Directions to 1 Zara Court via M1 Freeway (Monash Freeway). Take exit on to Cardinia Road. Take first left on to Bridge Road. Take third exit (right) at the first roundabout. Here you will find the complex and 1 Zara Court is the first townhouse on the left. If you want to type an address into google maps type Niki Place, Officer - it is directly opposite this road.

PENCIL IN PENSHURST
"So you want Timbertop but can't afford it? Well now you can."
Just as prices in Timbertop have seemingly passed you, this eye-catching four-bedroom home appears. One of the most affordable Timbertop properties to hit the market in recent memory. And what's even better, it's brand new.
Engineered and built with care and perfection, the creative floor plan will leave you awe-struck. Walking distance to shops and public transport and with new schools approved for the area you can't deny life if better in Timbertop.
The property features:
- Four bedrooms, master with en-suite and walk-in robe;
- Formal living area;
- Open plan living/dining room with upgraded floating floors throughout;
- Modern kitchen with thick, stone benches, large cooktop and trendy pendants;
- Ducted heating;
- High ceilings;
- Double car garage with internal access;
- Low maintenance landscaping plus decked area with bamboo-featured backdrop.

LAVISH LAGOON
"Why build, when your dream house is right here!"
One of Officer's most affordable properties in one of Officer's most expensive areas. Undoubtably Arena Estate sits aloft the hierarchy when it comes to Officer's estates. So it's incredible to find a gem like Lagoon at this price range.
Walking distance to Cardinia train station, schools and Arena shopping centre, the location at Lagoon is hard to argue.
The house itself features:
- Three bedrooms, master with en-suite and walk-in robe;
- Two distinct living areas including an open plan living/dining room;
- Modern kitchen with ample bench space;
- Heating and cooling;
- Single car garage;
- Decked backyard and landscaped front yard.
Get in as this property won't last long.

IT'S GAME TIME IN HARLEM
"You don't need to be a Harlem Globetrotter to know this is the winner"
It's game 7. Everything you have done up to this point leads you to where you are now. You're presented with the perfect shot. Do you take it?
When a property like this comes to the market you know you have to be on your game. Located in the ballin' Park Central estate, the property is close to shops, schools and public transport.
The house itself is a winner too, featuring:
- Four bedrooms, master with en-suite and walk-in robe;
- Open plan living/dining room;
- Theatre room;
- Rumpus room;
- Modern kitchen with oversized stone bench-tops and upgraded appliances;
- Double car garage and side access;
- Heating and cooling;
- Alfresco and decked-entertaining area;
- Massive block, spanning over 530sqm!
Beat the buzzer on this one.
